Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在薩凡納的兩條腿的人懂禮貌\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}than most Savannah people walking around upon two.
