Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"這條河屬于我們  我們來了"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"The river belonged to us, and we to it."
