Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對最優秀的獵人來說\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and for the very best hunters,
