Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不應該說出\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you have a duty towards avoiding
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這么諷刺的話\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}such sarcastic constructions.
