Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能反抗生命的本意\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We cannot cross the cause why we were born.
