Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多是傳言\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lies substantially.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你不是這條河上最好的向導\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So you aren't the best guide on the river then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是向導\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, I'm no guide at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打獵為生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am a market hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  你是獵人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, you're the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛好有位客人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I happen to have a house guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位來自弗吉尼亞州的紳士\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a gentleman from Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是斯圖爾特·格雷厄姆爵士的兒子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's the son of Sir Stuart Graham,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們親密的朋友和同僚\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}close friend and colleague,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想在河上打獵\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and he'd like to hunt our river.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便誰都可以帶他\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Any fool can find it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要隨便誰\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not looking for just any fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要最好的跟著\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm looking for the best fool going,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說你是最好的  是嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and they say that's you. Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一天的向導\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A day as a guide
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說損失重大\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}is a significant loss of production from my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錢不是問題\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Money's no object.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是誰都不許碰我的槍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but no one touches my guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我的狗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}or my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了  那我們就這么說定了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Splendid. Then we have a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很理解你的姿態\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your gesture is deeply appreciated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證  格雷厄姆先生裝備精良\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I assure you, Mr. Graham will come well-equipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個箱子是弗吉尼亞州長送我的禮物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That bag was a gift from the Governor of Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真該好好抱著\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then it should hold up just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你們在弗吉尼亞是怎么做的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know how you do this in, uh, Virginia,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在這  我們從來不敲鑼打鼓去打獵\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but here, we prefer to come unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I assure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經在印度和非洲打過獵\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've hunted India, Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我的副手一直\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My steady companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是來打獵\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you here to hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是來向我的狗秀出身的  格雷厄姆先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}or to impress the dog with your pedigree, Mr. Graham?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我的消息沒錯  我確定沒錯\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If my sources are correct, and I'm sure they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人有點矛盾  艾倫先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you're a bit of a paradox, Mr. Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是出國讀過書的人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You were educated abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是我的母校牛津大學的高材生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}at my alma mater, Oxford, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家喻戶曉的"野牛比爾"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Known as Buffalo Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N美国陆军侦察兵  曾在八个月内猎杀近五千头野牛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟是艾倫莊園的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}yet you are the descendent
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一繼承人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and sole inheritor of the Allen plantation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一介布衣\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm, uh, but a laborer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己的雙手討生活\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I earn that I eat, get that I wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與世無爭\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}owe no man hate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清心寡欲\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}envy no man's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知足\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Content...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常樂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}with my harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂莊園主出身\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Truly of the manor born,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然找個黑鬼做副手\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and yet you choose a Negro as your steady companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪斯塔布斯先生要大老遠跑去弗吉尼亞\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No wonder Mr. Stubbs sent all the way to Virginia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物色良婿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to find a suitor for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll do no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向斯塔布斯小姐承諾過\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I promised Miss Stubbs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要給她打只新鮮的野味\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a fresh bird for her table.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得保證我履行我的諾言\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It is your job to ensure that I keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得提醒你  你只是個拿錢辦事的向導\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}May I remind you that you are a paid guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好獵人舉了槍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No good hunter takes a shot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定彈無虛發\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}unless he knows he can't miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會有好下場\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You have not heard the last of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕斯塔布斯先生要找你麻煩嘍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You likely stirred up trouble now with Mr. Stubbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是有個表親在斯塔布斯家做廚子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't you have a cousin that cooks for Stubbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是有\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Not saying I don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她從來不跟我談起她與她無關的事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but she'd never talk about nothin' wasn't her business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  你也一樣\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's right. You, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你對斯塔布斯家的小姐一無所知\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's why you wouldn't know nothin' about Stubbs' daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把萊納家小伙兒迷得顛三倒四那妞么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The one that turned down Lynah's boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你表親絕對沒跟你說過這事兒\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Which your cousin never told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呦喂  居然自己尋著路回來了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Doodly doo, found his way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  悠著點兒\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, sir, account for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好  治安官先生  斯塔布斯先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Evening, Mr. Sheriff, Mr. Stubbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們說好了  艾倫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We had a deal, Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是說好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說要帶一位紳士到河上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To take a gentleman on the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  格雷厄姆先生根本不是什么紳士\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, Mr. Graham proved to be no gentleman at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恐怕他羞辱了您\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}See, I feared he'd bring embarrassment to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和您可愛的家人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and your lovely family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他大放闕詞說他一心覬覦令愛\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}boasting as it were over his intentions towards your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毅然決然拒絕帶路\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I--I--I resolutely refused
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不能用您的錢助紂為虐  先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to take a cent of your money, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能借一步嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please, if you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我的判斷沒錯的話\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I had exercised my better judgment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全可以避免\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you would not have been exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入如此尷尬的境地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to this public embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿聞其詳\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您如果想要野鴨  只管開口\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd be pleased if you'd take a pair of mallards for your table.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的廚子正愁沒鴨子下鍋呢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Our cook does do wonders with waterfowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一早給您送去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}First thing in the morning, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎  嘎  嘎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Quack quack quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么風把你吹來了啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What happy accident brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應給令尊送新鮮的野鴨來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I promised your father some fresh duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出你很守信\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A promise well kept, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還帶了你的小伙伴來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, you brought your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像挺高興見到我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He seems glad to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樣子雖呆  腦子聰明\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's smarter than he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保不齊它還會引用莎士比亞呢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Next thing I know, he'll be quoting Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.15,0:24:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請轉告令尊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please tell your father
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.32,0:24:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把子彈從鴨子身體里取出來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to remove the shot from the birds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.59,0:24:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者告訴廚師  隨便你了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}or tell your cook, whatever you plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日安  斯塔布斯小姐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good day, Miss Stubbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.60,0:24:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生  我想邀請\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. Allen, I wish to inquire, uh--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.03,0:24:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守信之人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A man of his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.37,0:24:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我此前還猶豫是否應該讓艾倫先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was on the verge of asking Mr. Allen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.08,0:24:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做我們的向導\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for a guide on the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.45,0:24:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫先生  我還從來沒在河上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You see, Mr. Allen, I've never seen the city
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細欣賞過這個城市\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}from the perspective of the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說景色非常美\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I'm told it's quite beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親可不是劃船高手\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And Father here has no inclination towards rowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西  艾倫先生忙于事業  時間金貴\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lucy, I'm sure Mr. Allen's time would be better spent at his enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.06,0:24:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  沃德  謝謝你的鴨子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thanks very much, Ward, for the duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.96,0:25:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢肯定這會是相當美味的一餐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sure it will be a meal to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.80,0:25:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得為表感謝\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The least we can do then
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們至少應該邀請艾倫先生共進晚餐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}is invite Mr. Allen for supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.00,0:25:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周日吧  德索托\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sunday? The DeSoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午見\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Noon, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.07,0:25:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.61,0:25:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏拉圖曾經把人的心靈\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Plato likens the mind of man
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比喻成鳥兒的天堂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to an aviary of birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.59,0:25:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而鳥兒則是浩瀚無垠的知識\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and birds to kinds of knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.82,0:25:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我發覺知識真是令人琢磨不透\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I find it a queer thing, knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.53,0:25:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不論邏輯是多么的嚴密\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}because no matter how tight the logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.56,0:25:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是會有特例出現\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}there's always the errant fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}like--like--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.30,0:25:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一只孤雁\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}like a solitary bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.13,0:25:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開雁群  獨自踏上冒險之旅\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}separated from the flock in search of adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是鳥也有理性\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you suggesting birds can reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.54,0:25:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緊隨渴望的理性是什么呢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is reason next to yearning?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.75,0:25:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  跟我說說  艾倫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes. Well, ahem... tell me, Allen,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.39,0:26:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明是出國留學的高材生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}with all this foreign education under your belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.45,0:26:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么會自甘選擇\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}how is it you choose to subject yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.56,0:26:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚴酷的野外生活\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to the rigors of an outdoor life?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么要選擇壓抑閉塞的辦公室生活呢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why not embrace the joys of the airless boardroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.37,0:26:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不用擔心刮風下雨啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Well, the rewards are not subject to the whims of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.10,0:26:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人心的風雨比起來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But instead on the whims of man's nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.04,0:26:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自然界的風雨更易掌握\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I find nature's nature far more predictable
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.41,0:26:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加  坦城\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and far more, uh, honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.08,0:26:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾分道理\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  你畢竟還是有著\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Still, you do seem to have a talent
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演講和辯論的天賦\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for discourse and persuasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.99,0:26:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有幸曾在法庭上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I could see you being very successful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一睹你的風采\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in the courtroom, for instance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.76,0:26:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我年輕時  曾浪費大好時光\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}As a boy, I wasted many beautiful days
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.03,0:26:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在枯燥的律師辦公室工作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in a dusty law office,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.36,0:26:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是我父母的安排\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}by arrangement of my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一心想要我干這一行\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They were bent on my entering the profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.70,0:26:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追隨約翰·艾略特·沃德光輝的腳步是嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Following the footsteps of the Honorable John Eliot Ward, no less?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.70,0:26:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎從他那里繼承了一個\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You seem to have inherited from him
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.71,0:26:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫圣誕·穆特里的好黑奴\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a fine servant in Christmas Moultrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.21,0:27:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叔叔認為圣誕是極好的向導\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My uncle saw in Christmas an accomplished guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.99,0:27:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以聘請了他\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and he hired him for his services.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.75,0:27:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果非要說是繼承\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If anyone did the inheriting,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是圣誕繼承了我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}it was Christmas of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.16,0:27:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就非要打破常規  是吧  艾倫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You turn everything on its head, don't you, Allen?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叛逆\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Quite the rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.16,0:27:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得你說得太夸張了點\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And here I thought you'd been exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《奥赛罗》
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.47,0:27:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"男人應當言如其實"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Well, men should be what they seem."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.70,0:27:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"如若不然  此人定一無所是"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Or those that be not, would not they be none?"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.81,0:27:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這樣很好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I think it's absolutely delightful--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.15,0:27:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學者回歸自然\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a man of letters who's returned to nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頗有幾分"公民的不服從"之風骨\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And a sprinkle of civil disobedience for good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.30,0:27:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是在暗示\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you are suggesting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像現代版的梭羅  那你錯了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm some sort of contemporary Thoreau, you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.52,0:27:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N梭罗著有《论公民的不服从》  后隐居瓦尔登湖
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.09,0:27:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并無目的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have no agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.26,0:27:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是單純喜歡這種生活\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I simply prefer this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.53,0:27:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.97,0:27:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治安官從歐利希的店里搶走了我們的獵物\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The sheriff stole our order from Ehrlich's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.13,0:27:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. Ward?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.94,0:27:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老實工作  這算什么罪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am guilty of nothing but an honest day's work,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.46,0:27:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他居然從餐桌上搶走了別人的晚餐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}while he steals a meal right off a man's table.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.44,0:28:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mr. Ward!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想寫一篇社論投給報社\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have a good mind to write the editor of the paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為我不會寫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and don't think I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.45,0:28:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原諒我打擾了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.12,0:28:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得給報社投稿是個好主意\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I think writing to the paper's a fine idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.02,0:28:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯塔布斯小姐想請我們為她服務\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Miss Stubbs here hired our services.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.66,0:28:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.83,0:28:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  艾倫先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't worry, Mr. Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.23,0:28:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想為我的花園采集一些野花\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I simply wish to collect cuttings for my garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.57,0:28:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野花在城市的花園里能養好嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A wildflower can be cultivated in a city garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要栽培方法得當\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}With the right nurturing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.55,0:28:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什么不能被教養好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}most anything can be cultivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.65,0:28:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先把這些獵物送到德索托\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I better get these birds here over to the DeSoto
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.64,0:28:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免得治安官把它們也拿走了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}before the Sheriff lock them up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.89,0:28:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午愉快  斯塔布斯小姐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good afternoon, Miss Stubbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.70,0:28:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的圣誕\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.64,0:29:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過藝術家們的描繪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've seen artists' renderings,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.35,0:29:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒想到它會這么美\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.42,0:29:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同泛舟于星河之上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's like floating on a sea of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.29,0:29:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這香氣\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And that perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.03,0:29:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像星星是由糖果做成的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's like stars made of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.70,0:29:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星島\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Starry archipelagoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.14,0:29:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極美星空\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}raving skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.34,0:29:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,極美星空\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Raving skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親在我的花園里建了一座日光浴室\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My father built a solarium for my garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.21,0:29:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小時候  不能隨意出門\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I was a little girl, I couldn't be outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.32,0:29:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那日光浴室大得像永遠填不滿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and the solarium seemed impossibly large to fill,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.49,0:29:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我畫得滿溢出來了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but I filled it till bursting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.26,0:29:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等滿到沒有地方可以畫畫后\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And when there was no more room for planting,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.99,0:30:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就躺在地板中央\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I laid down in the middle of the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.66,0:30:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在花叢之下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}buried beneath the flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.77,0:30:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想象我自己正在飛翔\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and imagined I was flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.50,0:30:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛毯\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A flying carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.77,0:30:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道瓦斯涅佐夫的畫作\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know Vasnetsov's painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.08,0:30:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.88,0:30:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父親認識俄國大使\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My father knew the Russian Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾繪聲繪色地描述過那幅畫的每個細節\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He described it in such vivid detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.09,0:30:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我感覺就像是親眼所見一般\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I felt like I'd seen it with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.06,0:30:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定認識俄國大使吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, you must have known the Russian Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.73,0:30:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親說你在俄國生活過\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Father says you were in Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.99,0:30:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次藏在花叢下的時候\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The first time I disappeared beneath the flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.27,0:30:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母找不到我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}my parents couldn't find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.30,0:30:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親差點心臟病發\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Father nearly had a heart attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.38,0:30:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要保護我的整個人生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He'd spent my whole life trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.97,0:30:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不受各種他所想象出的恐怖傷害\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}protect me from all kinds of imagined horrors,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我卻憑空消失了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and there I had vanished into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的避難所\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It was my refuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.17,0:31:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是野鳥的話  你抓不住我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I were a bird, you wouldn't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.84,0:31:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認得出誘餌\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You see, I recognize a decoy when I see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.82,0:31:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我會是什么樣的鳥呢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So, what kind of bird would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.25,0:31:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.17,0:31:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是一只野鳥  而你在狩獵我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I were a bird and you were hunting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.40,0:31:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會是什么樣的鳥\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}what would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.73,0:31:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野鴨\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A mallard.
