Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.52,0:47:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas.
