Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.31,0:48:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我不獵鴨除非太陽從西邊出來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hell will freeze over before they take mine.
