Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.83,0:48:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我們不能反抗生命的本意"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We cannot cross the cause why we were born.
