Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.89,1:03:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有逃避\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm doin' no such thing.
