Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.83,1:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說你在逃避我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't mean from me.
