Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.37,1:03:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解你  沃德·艾倫\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I see you, Ward Allen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.13,1:03:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的能力\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I see what you're capable of,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.84,1:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得出你現在離目標有多遠\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I see how far you've missed the mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.60,1:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親愛的  你在質疑我的槍法嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sweetheart, you questioning my marksmanship?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.04,1:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在質疑你的選擇\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I question your choices,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.11,1:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那些會讓你英年早逝的選擇\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}especially the ones that will send you to an early grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.78,1:03:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人  你當我是你的哈巴狗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Woman, you'd have me your lap dog,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.38,1:03:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在你的腳邊  唯命是從\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}sittin' at your heels, fetchin' at your command.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.92,1:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴你  大小姐\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I tell you what, little lady,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.32,1:03:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連獵犬也有自己的本能\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}even a retriever must have its own instincts,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.59,1:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按自己的意愿行動\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}act on its own accord,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.16,1:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要它是只稱職的獵犬\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}if it's to be worth its salt.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.69,1:03:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你自己比成狗還真是恰當\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Apropos you would liken yourself to a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.10,1:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪  我是自己的主宰\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Woof! I am my own master.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.63,1:04:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管我  女人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Leave me be, woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.77,1:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.34,1:04:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說話你就得聽\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You will if I say so.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.07,1:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要開槍打我嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So you'll shoot me?
