Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.79,1:04:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據其親眼所見\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and by her own eyewitness account,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.60,1:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她聲稱是我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}she has established it was I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.40,1:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準確無誤地射穿了這幅畫像的眼睛\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that shot out cleanly the eyes of this portrait
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.87,1:04:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在距離\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}from a distance of no less than...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.31,1:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五步之遠\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}15 paces,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.91,1:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的客廳是屋子里最大的房間\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}our parlor being the largest room in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.05,1:04:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,測試一個人是否清醒有很多方法\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There are many tests of a man's relative sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.49,1:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我告訴各位  這樣的槍法\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I offer to you that such a piece of marksmanship
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.62,1:05:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是測試方法之一\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}belongs among those tests.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.83,1:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由此只能推斷出\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It can only be deduced then
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.33,1:05:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位尊敬的夫人所做的陳述\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that the esteemed lady is incorrect
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.73,1:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自相矛盾\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in one statement or the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.63,1:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么是我醉了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Either I was drunk!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.34,1:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么是我開的槍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Or I made these shots.
