Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.75,1:05:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒謬了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is ridiculous!
