Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.43,1:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯然  我無須枉法或誤判\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And clearly, I would not have to bend the law or my judgment
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.96,1:05:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以直接駁回指控  放你走人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}very far to dismiss the charge and send you on your way.
