Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.44,1:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.07,1:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我發現為了公眾安全的利益\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, I find it in the interest of public safety
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.98,1:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須判你有罪\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to call you guilty...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.38,1:05:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.78,1:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判你入獄十天\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and put you in jail for 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.85,1:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽啊  聽啊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hear, hear!
