Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.08,1:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-這是暴行  -上前來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- This is an atrocity. - Approach.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.48,1:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就上前\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Approach now.
