Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.32,1:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是你  我會把這十天用來\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I were you, I would spend those 10 days
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.69,1:06:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用文字構建一個王國\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}using my way with words to conjure up one big Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.33,1:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱自己得到救贖\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}come prayer for your salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.80,1:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  沃德·艾倫  錯了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I, Ward Allen, was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.51,1:07:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  沃德·艾倫  也許錯了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I, Ward Allen, may have been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.48,1:07:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你去查看\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Before you check to see
