Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.85,1:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想強調  我將會\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}let me emphasize that I would do
