Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.23,1:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我選了另一條\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and I took the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.94,1:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許這個結果無法避免\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Perhaps this is an inevitable result,
