Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.35,1:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些接受世事起伏的人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}those who accepted that the affairs of men
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.33,1:08:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像一條河流\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}are like those of a river,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里  歲月是生命的終極塑造者\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}where time and tide are the ultimate shapers of a life,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.26,1:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里  繁衍  遷徙  甚至是死亡\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}where procreation, migration, and even death
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.80,1:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆由著上帝的意愿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}are spokes of the same wheel
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.88,1:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著歷史的車輪滾滾前行\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that turns in heaven's vault just the way it should.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.97,1:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一些人卻決意要\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But there are others who are determined
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.27,1:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重造車輪  逆流而上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to reshape that wheel and turn back the tide,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.85,1:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們似乎已經準備好了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and they appear ready to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.68,1:08:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他們是對的  他們也這么做了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe they are right, representing as they do,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.22,1:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口涌起的沖動\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}an impulse in the breast of man
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.25,1:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驅動著人類無止境工業化的腳步\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that drives our species toward restless industry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.16,1:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們的存在是為了再造一切\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe we are here to remake everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.79,1:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重塑一切\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}reshape everything,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.93,1:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造我們自己對于完美的新理念\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}create our own new idea of perfection
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.70,1:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把上帝的旨意留在歷史的陰影之中\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and leave God's idea to the dim shades of history.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.40,1:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我  一直在與新理念作斗爭\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And maybe I, having fought against that new idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.74,1:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕那理念\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}rejected that idea,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.88,1:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得那理念可憎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}found that idea abhorrent,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.55,1:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我錯了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}maybe I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.68,1:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我并不這么認為\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I do not think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.85,1:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我相信  如果人類整體取得了進步\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Because I believe if we have grown as a species,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.05,1:09:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為承受了野性的洗禮\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}it has been because of the test of wildness,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.49,1:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們將野性重塑成溫和\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and if we succeed in remaking wildness into mildness,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.56,1:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們將走向衰落\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}then we will begin to diminish.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.07,1:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我所做的一切換來的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But all I have accomplished
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.97,1:09:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是雙傷痕累累的拳頭\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}is a broken knuckle or two
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.37,1:09:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷害了我和我的愛人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and hurting myself and my own
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.51,1:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非我的本意目標\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}more than those who are the target of my calumny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.78,1:09:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  也許我應該\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So, perhaps I do better
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.41,1:09:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉆研那些書卷\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to take my pokes on these pages
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.38,1:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且聽從莎翁的指引\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and take direction from the Bard--
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.65,1:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"讓你的墨水里摻滿怨毒"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Let there be gall enough in thy ink."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.65,1:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N出自莎士比亚《第十二夜》
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.22,1:10:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得一試\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.09,1:10:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N萨凡纳市立监狱
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.67,1:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  讀了我的文章嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did you read my article?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.44,1:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.74,1:10:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.91,1:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.02,1:10:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再受屈了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I won't be disgraced again.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.93,1:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為一個母親那樣不合適\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not befitting a mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.96,1:10:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊森醫生已經確定了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Doctor Bryson is sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.47,1:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.33,1:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別急著說話  沃德\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't speak right now, Ward.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.14,1:10:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你仔仔細細地想想你現在的感受\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I want you to think very, very carefully about how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.11,1:10:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我可不能忍受\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}because I can't bear for you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.14,1:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我說謊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}anything less than God's own truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.53,1:11:11.36,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, bring me a gator *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.36,1:11:14.03,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Girl, when you come off the island *
