Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.81,1:11:29.21,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.21,1:11:31.55,Lyric,NTP,0,0,0,,* Oh, girl, when you come off the island *
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.55,1:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配額就這些了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's the quota.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.49,1:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歐利希店要的十二只\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}12 for Ehrlich's store,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.09,1:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德索托要的二十只\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}20 for the De Soto.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.56,1:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  他們會把這些野鴨子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Next thing you know, they'll make us buy
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.73,1:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過雜貨店再賣給我們\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the duck we shot back from the grocery store,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.26,1:11:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且價格是我們賣給他們的兩倍\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}twice what they paid us in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.97,1:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.74,1:11:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看那個\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Would you look at that!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.57,1:11:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西那天看到的船\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lucy's barge.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.61,1:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西打中了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lucy hit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.22,1:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.15,1:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是這艘船最傳奇的故事了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}One of the more improbable stories this old boat's got to tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.02,1:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這船還能航行嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You reckon she's seaworthy?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.59,1:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說漂浮  那應該可以\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It'll float, that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.23,1:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  白櫟木\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas, white oak.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.17,1:12:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗吉尼亞的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Virginia.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.09,1:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候約翰叔叔帶我去過里士滿\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uncle John took me to Richmond when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.09,1:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N美国内战时南方联邦的首都
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.45,1:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我戰爭快爆發了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Told me the aggression was coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.05,1:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你講過我的樹屋嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I ever tell you about my tree house?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.22,1:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰叔叔建的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uncle John built it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.62,1:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝爾曼開近的時候爬上艾倫樹屋\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Came up to Allen Station when Sherman got near.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.62,1:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}\N美国内战将军  以焦土政策闻名
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.86,1:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嚇得半死\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was scared half to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.99,1:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說如果北方佬把大房子都燒了  我們就住在這里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He said we'd live in it, the Yankees burn the big house down.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.31,1:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你目睹過內戰吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You must have seen the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.91,1:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有  先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, sir.
