Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.54,1:30:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  沃德先生\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Evenin', Mr. Ward.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.80,1:31:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克  我得確認下\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Jack, I just gotta confirm,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.77,1:31:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把圣誕趕出去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you got Christmas off the land.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.14,1:31:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊  我一直在考慮這事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Listen, Roy, I've been thinking about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.11,1:31:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕已經95歲了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas is 95 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.00,1:32:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能會活到105歲\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Probably gonna see 105.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.31,1:32:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在圣誕節那天出生于[佛州]馬爾伯里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was born on Mulberry on Christmas day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.98,1:32:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那個莊園最后的幸存者了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He is the last surviving member of that plantation.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.28,1:32:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是家人\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's not family.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.09,1:32:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是血親\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Not blood,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.29,1:32:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但被釋黑奴是有權利的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but freed slaves have rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.72,1:32:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰·艾略特·沃德親自立下的契約\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}John Eliot Ward wrote that deed himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.36,1:32:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是關鍵  杰克\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That ain't the point, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.93,1:32:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  圣誕都照顧不了自己\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Besides, Christmas can't even take care of himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.43,1:32:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不給他送吃的  他可能都餓死了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He'd probably starve to death if you weren't feeding him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.14,1:32:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為你會把這酒留到特別的時刻\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thought you were gonna save that for a special occasion?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.77,1:32:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比現在更特別的時刻了  羅伊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There's--there's nothing as special as the present, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.65,1:32:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來問問你\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.09,1:32:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有停下來仔細聽過以前黑奴唱的歌\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You ever stop and listen to the words of the old Negro songs?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.59,1:32:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們唱的我一句都聽不懂\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Can't understand a word they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.06,1:32:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唱首給你聽\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me sing one for you.
