Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.66,1:33:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個好人  杰克\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're a good man, Jack...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.53,1:33:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但記住我的話\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but mark my word,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.10,1:33:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的正是\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}what you said is exactly what you're going to find one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.87,1:33:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你無法阻擋時間\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You can't hold back time.
