Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.95,1:35:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的槍與雄辯已無用武之地  沃德\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've nothing left to prove with guns and bluster, Ward.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.09,1:35:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換種武器吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Try a different weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.20,1:35:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我寫過幾十篇關于狩獵的文章\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've written dozens of articles on shooting
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.44,1:35:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有超過兩倍的抨擊愚蠢狩獵法令的文章\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and twice more than that lambasting the damn fool game laws.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.71,1:35:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概比任何人都懂如何引經據典\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I probably know more quotes from English letters than any man,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.71,1:35:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用扯牛津那套\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}save an Oxford don.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.45,1:35:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以說出\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.33,1:35:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數十種羽毛的名字  顏色  用途與用法\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the name, color, use, and disposition of a dozen type of feathers,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.02,1:35:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少數十種水鳥的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and at least that many species of waterfowl.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.63,1:35:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己收集了很多南方聯邦的錢\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have a collection of Confederate money I saved myself,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.57,1:35:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從戰爭結束前就開始攢了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}beginning before the war ended...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.87,1:35:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有積攢了一輩子的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and a lifetime of practical experience
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.33,1:35:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在當今世上幾乎毫無用處的實踐經驗\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}having virtually no value in the world today.
