Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.65,1:36:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那該死的一切將我沖上了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and the damn thing has washed me up
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.48,1:36:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也辨認不出的城市岸邊\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}on the bank of a city I no longer recognize,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.38,1:36:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里住滿了我未曾邀請的人們\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}inhabited by people I don't remember inviting here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.62,1:36:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了那么多次\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All those arguments won,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.79,1:36:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果現在看來我贏錯了地方\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and now it seems I've misplaced my winnings.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.60,1:36:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣吧\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.67,1:36:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里是我曾泛舟的地方\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is where I pulled my skiff.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.40,1:37:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕  你懶到都不偶爾捅一捅火了嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas, you too lazy to poke at a fire once in a while?
