Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.44,1:37:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說除非分圣誕一片才行\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I said only on condition Christmas gets a slice.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.55,1:37:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.09,1:37:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讀了沃德在報紙上的最后一篇文章\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I read Ward's last article in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.49,1:37:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.80,1:38:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小杰克\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Little Jack,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.80,1:38:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫在理發椅上睡著了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ward Allen fell to sleep in the barber chair,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.81,1:38:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在那之前  他立下了規矩\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but not before he laid down the law.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.65,1:38:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  絕對不能\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He say don't lay a finger
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.55,1:38:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動他的胡子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}upon his mustache.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.77,1:38:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"俄國大使對沃德·艾倫說\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"And the Ambassador told Ward Allen,
