Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.22,1:38:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會親自把你押到沙皇面前\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I will deliver you to the Tsar myself
