Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.93,1:39:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然一個生來是莊園主\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"and although one to the manor born
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.67,1:39:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而另一個是奴隸出身\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"and the other born to slavery,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.10,1:39:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們卻成了性情相投的摯友\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"they were kindred spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.99,1:39:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小  我就和圣誕一起打獵\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"As a child, I hunted with Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.08,1:39:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河面上忙碌了一天后\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"After a long day on the river,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.38,1:39:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕會坐在壁爐前的搖椅上\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Christmas would sit in his rocker before the fireplace,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.68,1:39:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凝視著沃德的照片\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Gazing up at the picture of Ward,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.18,1:39:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地  細細地\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and with delicate slowness..."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.19,1:39:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講他的白人朋友"\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"talk of his white friend."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.09,1:39:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣誕講了一個故事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, Christmas told a story,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.22,1:39:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都一模一樣的故事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}he told it exactly the same every time,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.60,1:39:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字字不差\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}not a word out of place.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.04,1:39:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有一個故事他從來都沒有講給我聽過\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But there was one story he would never tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.87,1:39:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問了他幾百次\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I must have asked a hundred times,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.64,1:39:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃德·艾倫是怎么死的\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}how did Ward Allen die?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.65,1:39:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為他是想自己默默悼念\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I figured he'd go to his grave without me knowin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.75,1:39:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒意識到\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I didn't see
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.92,1:40:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這一生中他都在告訴我這個故事\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that he's been tellin' me my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.79,1:40:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And now, well...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.23,1:40:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他一直撐著活下去\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I think he was just holdin' on
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.87,1:40:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了等我明白\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}till I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.60,1:40:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你明白了嗎\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.34,1:40:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  兒子\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yes, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.91,1:40:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我明白了\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I think I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.52,1:41:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就該帶你來這里\N{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fs14}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I should have brought you here before.
